summary: This is an email from July 10, 2020, transmitting a document production in response to a grand jury subpoena issued on June 29, 2020. The email includes attachments with password-protected documents and a cover letter, indicating compliance with a subpoena request.

keyFacts: A grand jury subpoena was issued on June 29, 2020, indicating ongoing legal proceedings related to the Epstein case.
On July 10, 2020, a document production was submitted in response to the subpoena, showing compliance with legal requests.
The document production was password-protected and transmitted via email with attachments, highlighting secure handling of sensitive materials.
